config CUSTOM_KERNEL_GESTURE_SENSOR
	bool "mediatek gesture sensor tag"
	help
	  Kernel space support gesture sensor driver.
	  If the platform is supported for gesture, this
	  configuration should be configured, and the gesture
	  driver configuration should be configured as well.

config CUSTOM_KERNEL_GLANCE_GESTURE_SENSOR
	bool "mediatek glance gesture sensor type"
	help
	  Kernel space glance gesture sensor driver.
	  If the platform is supported for glance gesture, this
	  configuration should be configured, and the glance gesture
	  driver configuration should be configured as well.

