	bool "mediatek answer call sensor type"
	help
	  Kernel space answer call sensor driver.
	  If the platform is supported for answer call, this
	  configuration should be configured, and the answer call
	  driver configuration should be configured as well.

config CUSTOM_KERNEL_WAKE_GESTURE_SENSOR
	bool "mediatek wake gesture sensor type"
	help
	  Kernel space wake up gesture sensor driver.
	  If the platform is supported for wake gesture, this
